title: 15K Bean ????
body:
THis is asking what we do with the BEANs we have in the MSig.

NOTE: 15k *.15 = 2250 Treasury share

* If SOW all the beans,, we can't pay anyone but its becomes 180K beans if and when the pod line clears

* If we SOW  2250 Beans they become 27K beans

* If we Silo, we hope it brrs above peg
